Package: rmd4mla
Title: Produce MLA-Style Documents with R Markdown
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Clawson", , "clawson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: For preparing MLA-formatted documents, this package provides knitr functions, user-facing R Markdown templates, and packaged templates in Latex and Open Document files. Using make4ht and tex4ht, it also provides a fuction for simple conversion to the Open Document standard, which allows for preparation of Microsoft Word files using Biblatex.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
